ASTM Compass.stanza_text:
Option CookiePassThrough
Title ASTM Compass (updated 20190729)
URL https://compass.astm.org
HJ compass.astm.org
DJ compass.astm.org
Find .indexOf("compass") > -1
Replace .indexOf(".") > -1
Find .indexOf("compass.astm.org") > -1
Replace .indexOf(".") > -1
Find domain=.astm.org
Replace domain=^d
Find host=.astm.org
Replace host=^d
Find imgloc != ""
Replace false
Find "url":"http://
Replace "url":"http://^A
